name: Striped Green Bird Shirt  XS
description:
This hand-screenprinted 100% cotton white and green striped shirt needs you! Dark green bird screenprinted on a women's size xs shirt from The Gap.

Care: My screenprinted garments may be washed in the gentle cycle of your washing machine and line-dried in order to preserve your garment for as long as possible.

Please note: If you like this pattern, but not the color or size, please let me know. In order to keep my shop and your purchases as environmentally sustainable as possible, all of my screenprint items are printed on upcycled garments, so each piece is one of a kind and almost zero-impact on the environment. If I don't have your size, please email me, and I'll work on a one of a kind piece for you!
